videos.headline: Pitt on the board with pick-6
videos.description: Pitt's Dane Jackson tips Quentin Harris' pass, Paris Ford makes a catch and returns it 26 yards to the house.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt on the board with pick-6) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Mack impresses with beautiful TD catch for Pitt
videos.description: Taysir Mack hauls in a 19-yard touchdown catch under pressure from Kenny Pickett to extend Pitt's lead over Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mack impresses with beautiful TD catch for Pitt) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Pitt's Ford fired up after targeting ejection
videos.description: Paris Ford is ejected in the final minutes of the fourth quarter after he's called for targeting a Duke receiver. He exits the field under protest and has to be lead off.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt's Ford fired up after targeting ejection) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Duke rallies in the second half, take lead in final 2 minutes
videos.description: Deon Jackson takes a pass from Quentin Harris 44 yards to the end zone to put Duke on top, erasing a 23-point deficit vs. Pitt.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Duke rallies in the second half, take lead in final 2 minutes) 2019/10/5
